                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "profile",
                    "text": "Home lab profile (2-3 nodes)."
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "profile",
                    "text": "Workshop profile (4+ nodes)."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "profile",
            "text": "Document your bill of materials: Pi 5 board, PoE+ HAT with M.2 slot, NVMe SSD, microSD card, PoE+ switch, Ethernet cable, and active cooling. Missing cooling is a hard stop.",
